{"tid":1683802,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全民磚頭  雞尾酒  計劃正式上線啦","createTime":"2019-10-30T19:57:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T09:13:49.000Z","uid":189309,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e8df8f354e91ef50914e67f47a5033a914850954","tid":1683802,"uid":189309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T19:57:58.000Z","msg":"身為一個抗爭者基本保護自己嘅措施一定要足夠，但係如何保護自己呢？只要每人手上有一舊磚頭足以產生巨大力量，尤其是高位伏擊。<br />\n<br />\n以裝備比較一定冇得同啲黑狗比，但係我哋人多同玩伏擊嘅機會亦可以多好多。<br />\n<br />\n只要全民武器在手一見到啲黑狗就衝埋去揼鳩佢，尤其是係單落喺車嘅黑狗，請佢飲支雞尾酒醒神又暢快。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ff037c78a49170d94dc4f209460461ca351a2b","tid":1683802,"uid":189309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T19:59:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d36b154460f37cc287e4cb459cc86de63a8aa7e","tid":1683802,"uid":300549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T20:04:28.000Z","msg":"唔磚頭罐裝咖啡都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1478978792539fbe34dc7e95e122fd43d05cfbdd","tid":1683802,"uid":189309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T20:13:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4a25b1c6a858c741d25fc98663980db15ae2bcf","tid":1683802,"uid":189309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T20:13:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ec198ab20f05ec8e3e3b62a831f9eba7fddeba3","tid":1683802,"uid":98993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T20:14:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d67d63bd339884aa4213d9f8ae710a12c1ee2e3","tid":1683802,"uid":189309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T08:51:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a24f46bff24abd0430203f177f687c0bce66398","tid":1683802,"uid":189309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T08:51:29.000